text: Gorchaki () is a rural locality (a village) in Mikyashevsky Selsoviet, Davlekanovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 120 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 25 km from Davlekanovo, 7 km from Mikyashevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Davlekanovsky District
title: Gorchaki
